[
  {
    "startTime": 7.6,
    "endTime": 9.8,
    "text": "Fuck."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 10.0,
    "endTime": 11.120000000000001,
    "text": "Hey, how are you holding up, Sadness?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 11.3,
    "endTime": 12.4,
    "text": "I know they got you working overtime."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 12.7,
    "endTime": 14.84,
    "text": "Ever since his wife left him, I just couldn't take a break."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 14.84,
    "endTime": 15.6,
    "text": "Dang, how long has it been?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 15.8,
    "endTime": 16.5,
    "text": "It's been months!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 16.8,
    "endTime": 17.1,
    "text": "Oh, dang."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 17.1,
    "endTime": 17.6,
    "text": "Here, let me see if I can..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 17.9,
    "endTime": 18.299999999999997,
    "text": "Ouch!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 18.5,
    "endTime": 19.3,
    "text": "Yeah, sorry."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 19.5,
    "endTime": 22.0,
    "text": "I wish I could help, but IT hasn't fixed my login credentials yet."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 22.0,
    "endTime": 23.0,
    "text": "Oh my god."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 23.0,
    "endTime": 24.0,
    "text": "Hey, what are you doing?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 24.0,
    "endTime": 25.0,
    "text": "I'm taking PTO."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 25.0,
    "endTime": 26.5,
    "text": "Wait, you can't just do that."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 26.6,
    "endTime": 27.3,
    "text": "You gotta get that approved first."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 27.5,
    "endTime": 28.0,
    "text": "I don't care."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 28.2,
    "endTime": 30.68,
    "text": "I don't care. These are unfair working conditions."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 30.68,
    "endTime": 33.439,
    "text": "You guys couldn't control his anger, and now I'm the one that has to clean up his mess."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 33.439,
    "endTime": 33.9,
    "text": "Okay, now."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 34.1,
    "endTime": 36.72,
    "text": "It was between spending time with her or the new Elden Ring DLC."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 36.72,
    "endTime": 37.72,
    "text": "I had to make a decision."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 37.72,
    "endTime": 39.3,
    "text": "But you didn't need to make him yell at her like that."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 39.5,
    "endTime": 41.84,
    "text": "Yeah, well, Joy made me do it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 41.6,
    "endTime": 43.959,
    "text": "Look, I just really want to play Elden Ring."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 43.959,
    "endTime": 44.0,
    "text": "You know what?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 44.2,
    "endTime": 45.959,
    "text": "I'm taking off indefinitely."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 49.6,
    "endTime": 51.800000000000004,
    "text": "Hey, um..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 52.0,
    "endTime": 52.9,
    "text": "Who are you?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 53.1,
    "endTime": 55.300000000000004,
    "text": "Oh, I'm the new temp covering for Sadness."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 55.2,
    "endTime": 56.2,
    "text": "You can call me Depression."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 56.2,
    "endTime": 57.2,
    "text": "Wow, that was quick."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 57.8,
    "endTime": 58.9,
    "text": "How long are you here for?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 59.0,
    "endTime": 59.4,
    "text": "I don't know."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 59.4,
    "endTime": 63.119,
    "text": "Could be a few days, weeks, months, or maybe until he has no reason to live."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 63.119,
    "endTime": 63.4,
    "text": "I don't know."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 63.6,
    "endTime": 64.0,
    "text": "Wait, what?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 64.2,
    "endTime": 65.60000000000001,
    "text": "Alright, let's see here."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 65.8,
    "endTime": 67.8,
    "text": "He's drinking orange juice?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 68.0,
    "endTime": 69.7,
    "text": "Yeah, we're gonna need something stronger than that."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 69.9,
    "endTime": 70.9,
    "text": "Wait, wait, wait. What are you doing?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 71.0,
    "endTime": 71.9,
    "text": "It's still early in the day."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 72.1,
    "endTime": 74.1,
    "text": "Oh, relax. He just needs to loosen up."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 74.1,
    "endTime": 75.1,
    "text": "What do you got him doing now?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 75.2,
    "endTime": 76.5,
    "text": "Just scrolling down memory lane."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 76.7,
    "endTime": 79.4,
    "text": "I don't think scrolling through old Facebook photos is good for him right now."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 79.6,
    "endTime": 82.3,
    "text": "Hey, when was the last time you got any, you know..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 82.6,
    "endTime": 84.0,
    "text": "What do you mean?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 85.2,
    "endTime": 86.3,
    "text": "Yeah, hey man."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 86.5,
    "endTime": 89.0,
    "text": "Can you come up here for a second?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 89.0,
    "endTime": 90.0,
    "text": "What'd you need, Depression?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 90.2,
    "endTime": 91.4,
    "text": "Aroused?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 91.3,
    "endTime": 92.6,
    "text": "Joy, is that you?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 92.7,
    "endTime": 93.3,
    "text": "Oh, wow."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 93.3,
    "endTime": 94.2,
    "text": "Long time no see, man."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 94.2,
    "endTime": 95.0,
    "text": "It's been a while."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 95.0,
    "endTime": 96.1,
    "text": "When was the last time we met?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 96.1,
    "endTime": 96.89999999999999,
    "text": "The wedding?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 97.0,
    "endTime": 97.6,
    "text": "I think it was the honeymoon."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 97.6,
    "endTime": 98.6,
    "text": "Oh, wait, wait. No, no, no."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 98.7,
    "endTime": 99.5,
    "text": "That time in Peru."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 99.5,
    "endTime": 100.2,
    "text": "Oh, yeah. Peru."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 100.4,
    "endTime": 101.2,
    "text": "Yeah, good times."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 101.2,
    "endTime": 102.0,
    "text": "Good times."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 102.0,
    "endTime": 103.2,
    "text": "So, you know Depression?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 103.4,
    "endTime": 106.0,
    "text": "Oh, we worked on a few projects together back in the fantasy department."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 106.0,
    "endTime": 107.2,
    "text": "Oh, what projects?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 107.2,
    "endTime": 108.0,
    "text": "Let's not bring that up right now."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 108.3,
    "endTime": 111.0,
    "text": "Anyways, do you know anyone he used to hook up with?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 111.0,
    "endTime": 112.1,
    "text": "Any old flames or exes?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 112.3,
    "endTime": 112.89999999999999,
    "text": "Nope."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 112.9,
    "endTime": 114.0,
    "text": "Has he checked his Facebook?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 114.2,
    "endTime": 115.5,
    "text": "He's doing that right now."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 115.7,
    "endTime": 118.12,
    "text": "Um, guys, I don't think this is the time for him to hook up with anyone."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 118.12,
    "endTime": 118.30000000000001,
    "text": "Trust me."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 118.5,
    "endTime": 120.12,
    "text": "He just need to get his mind off the pain for a while."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 120.12,
    "endTime": 127.91900000000001,
    "text": "You know, I think what's best for him is that he should get back on a journey of self-love, you know? Like get back into his hobbies, reconnect with friends, you know?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 127.919,
    "endTime": 129.0,
    "text": "I think that would definitely help."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 129.0,
    "endTime": 129.7,
    "text": "Yeah, yeah, yeah."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 129.7,
    "endTime": 131.32,
    "text": "You're probably right."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 131.32,
    "endTime": 132.7,
    "text": "Wait, what's that?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 132.7,
    "endTime": 133.29999999999998,
    "text": "What's what?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 133.3,
    "endTime": 134.0,
    "text": "Whose page is that?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 134.0,
    "endTime": 135.52,
    "text": "Is that who I think it is?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 135.52,
    "endTime": 135.9,
    "text": "Oh, no."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 136.1,
    "endTime": 138.0,
    "text": "No, no, no, no, no, no, no. - Alright, it's game over."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 138.2,
    "endTime": 139.51999999999998,
    "text": "We're shutting this place down, boys. - No, no, no."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 139.8,
    "endTime": 140.70000000000002,
    "text": "Hold on, hold on. - No, no, no, no, no, no."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 140.9,
    "endTime": 141.8,
    "text": "It's no safe here.- I think we're safe."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 142.0,
    "endTime": 143.6,
    "text": "Let's just call it off. - Come on."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 143.6,
    "endTime": 144.9,
    "text": "I said no."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 144.9,
    "endTime": 146.52,
    "text": "All right, everyone, get out."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 146.52,
    "endTime": 146.9,
    "text": "Who are you?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 146.9,
    "endTime": 147.9,
    "text": "I am Insecurity."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 147.9,
    "endTime": 149.52,
    "text": "I'm here to stop this entire meltdown."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 149.52,
    "endTime": 155.8,
    "text": "Now, get out."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 155.8,
    "endTime": 156.9,
    "text": "All right, listen here."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 157.1,
    "endTime": 160.339,
    "text": "I'm gonna need you to suck it up because today is the day you're gonna become a man."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 160.339,
    "endTime": 161.82,
    "text": "From now on, the gym's your home."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 161.9,
    "endTime": 170.0,
    "text": "You're gonna be drinking protein shakes, listening to Andrew Tate podcasts, investing in Bitcoin, and then today, you're buying a Dodge Charger."
  }
]